    <stitle>No Idle APU/HVAC System - Repair Procedures - Diagnosing the Rotor</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="remove" graphiccount="1">
        <title>Diagnosing the Rotor</title>
        <figure id="f1603737" figsize="pg-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figg16/G1603737.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="502px"
                     scalefitheight="272px"/>
            <caption>Figure 34. Diagnosing the Rotor</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Visually inspect windings for dark streaks.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Place an ohmmeter across the solder connection of each diode. If the resistance does not
                compare with resistance values in test section of this manual, replace rotor.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Check bearing spin by hand. If it is rough, noisy or dry, replace bearing.</para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
